    <title>转二进制的python代码样例</title>
    <link href="https://aritz-real.github.io/2025/11/04/binary/"/>
    <id>https://aritz-real.github.io/2025/11/04/binary/</id>
    <published>2025-11-04T15:59:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-11-04T15:18:07.345Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>下面是信息考试想用python交作业的同学可以用的参考代码:(开源，自由转发)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">num=int(input())</span><br><span class="line">def calc(n):</span><br><span class="line">    if n == 0: return &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    return calc(n // 2) + str(n % 2)</span><br><span class="line">binary_str = calc(abs(num)) if abs(num) &gt; 0 else &quot;0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">print(binary_str if num &gt;= 0 else &#x27;-&#x27; + binary_str)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>(这个是精简版，里面用到了递归)<br>如果这个对你来说有些难以理解，还有一个稍微麻烦一点的(递归肯定跑不了了肯定得用):</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a=int(input())</span><br><span class="line">out=&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">def calc(num):</span><br><span class="line">    global out</span><br><span class="line">    if num==1:return 1</span><br><span class="line">    res=str(calc(num//2))</span><br><span class="line">    out=out+res</span><br><span class="line">    return num%2</span><br><span class="line">if a!=0:</span><br><span class="line">    res=str(calc(abs(a)))</span><br><span class="line">    out=out+res</span><br><span class="line">    if a&lt;0: out=&#x27;-&#x27;+out</span><br><span class="line">else: out=0</span><br><span class="line">print(out)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我个人觉得最好还是越精简越好(有强迫症没办法)</p><p>P.S. 这个题目其实有对应的python内置函数可以一步解决:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(format(int(input()),&#x27;b&#x27;))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
