  <entry>
    <title>关于个人主题的编写经验</title>
    <link href="https://aritz-real.github.io/2025/06/27/somecodes/"/>
    <id>https://aritz-real.github.io/2025/06/27/somecodes/</id>
    <published>2025-06-27T12:31:09.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-07-10T14:40:26.338Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>写了若干时间终于是把主题大框写出来了，记录一下编写的过程和一些坑。</p><h1 id="首先，得先熟练编写调试代码。"><a href="#首先，得先熟练编写调试代码。" class="headerlink" title="首先，得先熟练编写调试代码。"></a>首先，得先熟练编写调试代码。</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server (或者hexo s)</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>(我直接写一个<code>server.bat</code>和<code>update.bat</code>解决问题)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//server.bat</span><br><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">cd &quot;你的blog文件夹&quot;</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//update.bat</span><br><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">cd &quot;你的blog文件夹&quot;</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="主题文件夹配置"><a href="#主题文件夹配置" class="headerlink" title="主题文件夹配置:"></a>主题文件夹配置:</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">your-theme:</span><br><span class="line">    -layout:</span><br><span class="line">        -_partial           -放小部件的文件夹</span><br><span class="line">        -index.ejs          -主页代码</span><br><span class="line">        -layout.ejs         -主代码，下面有固定写法</span><br><span class="line">        -post.ejs           -文章页渲染代码，可以外挂article.ejs渲染文章内容</span><br><span class="line">        -其他文件...</span><br><span class="line">    -其他文件夹(个人添加，如js，css等)...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="注意事项和写法"><a href="#注意事项和写法" class="headerlink" title="注意事项和写法"></a>注意事项和写法</h1><p>当然，我发现不同的作者愿意用不同的编程语言写(我用的是ejs)<br>我不是很清楚用这些到底有什么区别(总之到最后就是用来渲染)，这些类型的文件实现的效果就是动态插入javascript内容，本质上没啥区别。<br>其实细品这么写比写html灵活多了<br>_partial这个文件夹一般不留空，大多数情况下你都得写点什么小组件(全堆一个文件里不好应用)</p><p>index.ejs看个人需求写，就跟写正常html一样的<br>但是index.ejs里面有一些注意点:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;button class=&quot;nav-button&quot; onclick=&quot;location.href=&#x27;&lt;%= url_for(&#x27;about/index&#x27;) %&gt;&#x27;&quot;&gt;About&lt;/button&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例如这句，url_for是请求对应文章url的函数，比如这个about，写好之后放在source里面就行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;% </span><br><span class="line">    const allPosts = site.posts.sort(&#x27;date&#x27;, -1).toArray(); //按时间降序排列</span><br><span class="line">    const articles = allPosts.filter(post =&gt; String(post.raw).indexOf(&quot;article&quot;)!=-1); </span><br><span class="line">    //筛选post.raw里面带有article的文章</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div id=&quot;articlesContent&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% articles.forEach(post =&gt; &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;a href=&quot;&lt;%= url_for(post.path) %&gt;&quot; class=&quot;article-item&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div class=&quot;article-title&quot;&gt;&lt;%= post.title %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div class=&quot;article-date&quot;&gt;&lt;%= date(post.date, &#x27;YYYY-MM-DD&#x27;) %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125;); %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这段代码上面是筛选(一定会用到的函数都在里面)，下面是html显示<br>const articles这句使用js的filter函数，匿名创建变量post来遍历allposts<br>判断遍历每次遇到的post是否满足需求，如果满足就加入变量articles(其实就是for循环的超级简化版)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">下面的部分应该无需赘述，通过函数名就能看懂是干啥的。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是article(或者是post)的一些必需函数:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```html</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- 文章头部 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;header class=&quot;article-header&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;h1 class=&quot;article-title&quot;&gt;&lt;%= page.title %&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;article-meta&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;span&gt;发布时间: &lt;%- date(page.date, &#x27;YYYY年MM月DD日&#x27;) %&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/header&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- 文章正文 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;article class=&quot;article-content&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- page.content %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/article&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我是分开写的，就是在post.ejs里面引用article.ejs渲染:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- 文章内容 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;article-container&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- partial(&#x27;_partial/artical&#x27;, &#123; post: page &#125;) %&gt; //得传参</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下面是重点(layout写法)，建议直接照搬照抄，细节自己改就行:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;html lang=&quot;&lt;%= config.language %&gt;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;title&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;% if (is_home()) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;%= config.title %&gt; | 主页</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;% &#125; else &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;%= page.title %&gt; | &lt;%= config.title %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body class=&quot;&lt;% if (is_post()) &#123; %&gt;post-page&lt;% &#125; %&gt;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- 动态内容切换区 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% if (is_home()) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(&#x27;index&#x27;) %&gt;  &lt;!-- 加载index.ejs内容 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; else &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(&#x27;post&#x27;, &#123;post: page&#125;) %&gt; &lt;!-- 加载post.ejs并传递文章数据 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- 共用页脚 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;footer&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        © &lt;%= new Date().getFullYear() %&gt; &lt;%= config.title %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/footer&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h1><p>这就是编写一个个人主题所需的一切了！当你想要传文章的时候就在_post文件夹里加文件就行<br>想要把不同的文章归档可以在tag里面加一些用于区分的文字(例如article为一类)<br>当然我的处理方法比较拙劣，如果你有更好的也可以。<br>当然，这不是结尾，你还得写一些必要的markdown渲染内容，这里不再赘述，这里可以考虑让deepseek代劳了。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
